      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor was super rushed and barely explained it. i looked it up online and some people say if the bacteria are dead, the medicine is just doing extra work for no reason and might mess up my gut health. if the skin is already clear, isn't the infection basically gone? i'd rather just stop now and save the rest of the pills.",
