      "content": "i mean i get the theory but honestly i'm already feeling 100% fine. if i stop now, i'm basically just avoiding unnecessary side effects like nausea or diarrhea that usually come with the later days of these things. like, if the bacteria are already gone, isn't it more scientifically sound to just stop? surely there's no real difference between stopping at day 3 or day 10 if the symptoms are totally gone.",
